Correlations of the RNAseq and TMT MS data with previously published data¶

This Python notebook includes the code that was used to correlate the RNA and protein remodeling during DNA limitation with previously published datasets in the literature.

Publication: Genome concentration limits cell growth and modulates proteome composition in Escherichia coli

def get_protein_slope_dict(dataframe):
    
    onen_dict = pd.Series(dataframe['Protien Slope (1-N)'].values, index=dataframe.Uniprot).to_dict()
    mltn_dict = pd.Series(dataframe['Protien Slope (multi-N)'].values, index=dataframe.Uniprot).to_dict()
    
    return onen_dict, mltn_dict

def assemgle_protein_slope_dataframe(dataframe_exp1, dataframe_exp2, rna_df):
    
    gene_name_to_id_dict = pd.Series(rna_df.gene_ID.values, index=rna_df.gene_name).to_dict()
    uniprot_to_gene_name_dict = pd.Series(dataframe_exp1['Gene name (primary )'].values, index=dataframe_exp1.Uniprot).to_dict()
    
    onen_dict_exp1, mltn_dict_exp1 = get_protein_slope_dict(dataframe_exp1)
    onen_dict_exp2, mltn_dict_exp2 = get_protein_slope_dict(dataframe_exp2)
    
    slope_df = pd.DataFrame()
    slope_df['Uniprot'] = np.unique(list(onen_dict_exp1.keys())+list(onen_dict_exp2.keys()))
    slope_df['slope_1N_exp1'] = slope_df.Uniprot.map(onen_dict_exp1)
    slope_df['slope_1N_exp2'] = slope_df.Uniprot.map(onen_dict_exp2)
    slope_df['slope_mltN_exp1'] = slope_df.Uniprot.map(mltn_dict_exp1)
    slope_df['slope_mltN_exp2'] = slope_df.Uniprot.map(mltn_dict_exp2)
    slope_df['gene_name'] = slope_df.Uniprot.map(uniprot_to_gene_name_dict)
    slope_df['gene_ID'] = slope_df.gene_name.map(gene_name_to_id_dict)
    
    return slope_df

def get_ion_intensity_and_ori_distance(misc_df, slope_df):
    
    ori_dict = pd.Series(misc_df['Circular distance from oriC'].values, index = misc_df['Entry']).to_dict()
    ion_dict = pd.Series(misc_df['Summed ion intensity / Length'].values, index = misc_df['Entry']).to_dict()
    
    slope_df['ori_distance'] = slope_df.Uniprot.map(ori_dict)
    slope_df['ion_intensity'] = slope_df.Uniprot.map(ion_dict)
    slope_df['mean_slope_1N'] = (slope_df['slope_1N_exp1']+slope_df['slope_1N_exp2'])/2
    slope_df['mean_slope_mltN'] = (slope_df['slope_mltN_exp1']+slope_df['slope_mltN_exp2'])/2
    
    return slope_df


def get_rates(rates_df, slope_df,
              prot_misc_df, rna_df):
    
    protein_conc_dict = pd.Series(rates_df['protein concentration [Pi] (1/µm3)'].values, index = rates_df['locus']).to_dict()
    rna_conc_dict = pd.Series(rates_df['mRNA concentration [mRi] (1/µm3)'].values, index = rates_df['locus']).to_dict()
    transl_init_dict = pd.Series(rates_df['translation inititation rate αpi (1/min)'].values, index = rates_df['locus']).to_dict()
    rna_degr_dict = pd.Series(rates_df['mRNA degradation rate, δi (1/min)'].values, index = rates_df['locus']).to_dict()
    transc_init_dict = pd.Series(rates_df['transcriptional initiation rate, αmi (1/min)'].values, index = rates_df['locus']).to_dict()
    promoter_on_dict = pd.Series(rates_df['promoter on-rate, ki (µm3/min)'].values, index = rates_df['locus']).to_dict()
    
    rna_df['protein_conc'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(protein_conc_dict)
    rna_df['rna_conc'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(rna_conc_dict)
    rna_df['translation_init'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(transl_init_dict)
    rna_df['transcription_init'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(transc_init_dict)
    rna_df['rna_degradation'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(rna_degr_dict)
    rna_df['promoter_on'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(promoter_on_dict)
    
    onen_slope_dict = pd.Series(slope_df.mean_slope_1N.values, slope_df.gene_ID).to_dict()
    mltn_slope_dict = pd.Series(slope_df.mean_slope_mltN.values, slope_df.gene_ID).to_dict()
    intensity_dict_prot = pd.Series(slope_df.ion_intensity.values, slope_df.gene_ID).to_dict()
    intensity_dict = pd.Series(prot_misc_df['Summed ion intensity'].values, index=prot_misc_df['Gene name']).to_dict()
    intensity_length_dict = pd.Series(prot_misc_df['Summed ion intensity / Length'].values, index=prot_misc_df['Gene name']).to_dict()
    ori_dict = pd.Series(prot_misc_df['Circular distance from oriC'].values, index=prot_misc_df['Gene name']).to_dict()
    
    rna_df['1N_protein_slope'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(onen_slope_dict)
    rna_df['mltN_protein_slope'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(mltn_slope_dict)
    rna_df['protein_ion_intensity'] = rna_df.gene_ID.map(intensity_dict_prot)
    rna_df['summed_ion_intensity'] = rna_df.gene_name.map(intensity_dict)
    rna_df['summed_ion_intensity_per_length'] = rna_df.gene_name.map(intensity_length_dict)
    rna_df['circular_ori_distance'] = rna_df.gene_name.map(ori_dict)
    rna_df['gene_length'] = rna_df.summed_ion_intensity/rna_df.summed_ion_intensity_per_length
    
    return rna_df
    

def density_scatter(x,y):
    xy = np.vstack([x,y])
    z = gaussian_kde(xy)(xy)
    return z

def plot_concentration_comparisons_with_literature(rna_data):
    
    plt.figure(figsize=(12,4))
    gs = matplotlib.gridspec.GridSpec(1, 5, height_ratios=[1], width_ratios=[1,0.1,0.5,1,0.1])
    gss = [plt.subplot(gs[0,0]),
           plt.subplot(gs[0,1]),
            plt.subplot(gs[0,3]),
            plt.subplot(gs[0,4])]
    one_axis = gss[0]
    cbar_one_axis = gss[1]
    two_axis = gss[2]
    cbar_two_axis = gss[3]
    
    plot_df = rna_data[rna_data['summed_ion_intensity_per_length']>0]
    spear_df = pd.DataFrame()
    spear_df['x'] = plot_df['summed_ion_intensity_per_length'].astype(float)
    spear_df['y'] = plot_df.protein_conc.astype(float)
    spear_df = spear_df.dropna()
    spear_df['z'] = density_scatter(np.log10(spear_df.x), np.log10(spear_df.y))
    print(plot_df.shape)
    
    im1 = one_axis.scatter(spear_df.x, spear_df.y, c=spear_df.z, cmap='cividis', s=2)
    one_axis.set_yscale('log')
    one_axis.set_xscale('log')
    cbar_one = plt.colorbar(im1, cax=cbar_one_axis)
    cbar_one.set_label('Density', rotation=90, fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    print(spearmanr(spear_df.x, spear_df.y))
    one_axis.set_xlabel('Summed ion intensity / gene Length', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    one_axis.set_ylabel('Protein concentration (1/um$^3$)\nBalakrishnan $et al$, 2022', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')

    
    plot_df = rna_data[rna_data['TPM_60min']>0]
    spear_df = pd.DataFrame()
    spear_df['x'] = plot_df['TPM_60min'].astype(float)
    spear_df['y'] = plot_df.rna_conc.astype(float)
    spear_df = spear_df.dropna()
    spear_df['z'] = density_scatter(np.log10(spear_df.x), np.log10(spear_df.y))
    print(plot_df.shape)


    im2 = two_axis.scatter(spear_df.x, spear_df.y, c=spear_df.z, cmap='cividis', s=2)
    two_axis.set_yscale('log')
    two_axis.set_xscale('log')
    cbar_two = plt.colorbar(im2, cax=cbar_two_axis)
    cbar_two.set_label('Density', rotation=90, fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    print(spearmanr(spear_df.x, spear_df.y))
    two_axis.set_xlabel('Transcripts per million\n(60min after induction)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    two_axis.set_ylabel('mRNA concentration (1/um$^3$)\nBalakrishnan $et al$, 2022', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')

def correlations_with_rate_statistics(rna_data):
    
    min_val, max_val = 0.15,0.9
    n = 10
    orig_cmap = plt.cm.binary
    colors = orig_cmap(np.linspace(min_val, max_val, n))
    short_cmap = matplotlib.colors.LinearSegmentedColormap.from_list("mycmap", colors)
    
    
    cmap_ = short_cmap
#     cmap_ = 'cividis'
    markercolor_ = 'orange'
    
    markersize_=15
    
    plt.figure(figsize=(15,12))
    gs = matplotlib.gridspec.GridSpec(2, 6, height_ratios=[1,1], width_ratios=[0.8,0.1,0.5]*2)
    gss = [plt.subplot(gs[0,0]),
           plt.subplot(gs[0,3]),
            plt.subplot(gs[1,0]),
              plt.subplot(gs[1,3])]
    
    # Image 1
    plot_df = rna_data.copy()
    spear_df = pd.DataFrame()
    spear_df['x'] = plot_df['transcription_init'].astype(float)
    spear_df['y'] = plot_df.RNA_slope.astype(float)
    spear_df = spear_df[spear_df.x>0]
    spear_df = spear_df.dropna()
    spear_df['z'] = density_scatter(np.log10(spear_df.x), spear_df.y)
    
    spear_df['log_x'] = np.log10(spear_df.x)
    spear_df['x_bin'] = pd.qcut(spear_df.x, 9)
    print(spear_df.x_bin.value_counts())
    mean_df = spear_df.groupby(spear_df.x_bin).mean()
    err_df = spear_df.groupby(spear_df.x_bin).sem()
    print(spear_df.shape)
    print(spearmanr(spear_df.x, spear_df.y))
    im1 = gss[0].scatter(spear_df.x, spear_df.y, c=spear_df.z, cmap=cmap_, s=markersize_)
    gss[0].errorbar(mean_df.x, mean_df.y, yerr=err_df.y,
            marker='o', markersize=10, markerfacecolor='none',ls='none', color=markercolor_)
    gss[0].set_xscale('log')
    cbar_one = plt.colorbar(im1, cax=plt.subplot(gs[0,1]))
    cbar_one.set_label('Density', rotation=90, fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    gss[0].set_xlabel('Transcription initiation rate (1/min)\nBalakrishnan $et al$, 2022', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    gss[0].set_ylabel('RNA slope - 1N cells', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    gss[0].axhline(0, color='black', linewidth=0.5)
    gss[0].set_ylim(-2,2)

    # Image 3
    plot_df = rna_data.copy()
    spear_df = pd.DataFrame()
    spear_df['x'] = plot_df['rna_degradation'].astype(float)
    spear_df['y'] = plot_df.RNA_slope.astype(float)
    spear_df = spear_df[spear_df.x>0]
    spear_df = spear_df.dropna()
    spear_df['z'] = density_scatter(np.log10(spear_df.x), spear_df.y)
    
    spear_df['log_x'] = np.log10(spear_df.x)
    spear_df['x_bin'] = pd.qcut(spear_df.x, 9)
    print(spear_df.x_bin.value_counts())
    print(spear_df.shape)
    mean_df = spear_df.groupby(spear_df.x_bin).mean()
    err_df = spear_df.groupby(spear_df.x_bin).sem()
    
    print(spearmanr(spear_df.x, spear_df.y))
    im3 = gss[1].scatter(spear_df.x, spear_df.y, c=spear_df.z, cmap=cmap_, s=markersize_)
    gss[1].errorbar(mean_df.x, mean_df.y, yerr=err_df.y,

    cbar_three = plt.colorbar(im3, cax=plt.subplot(gs[0,4]))
    cbar_three.set_label('Density', rotation=90, fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    gss[1].set_xlabel('mRNA degradation rate (1/min)\nBalakrishnan $et al$, 2022', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    gss[1].set_ylabel('RNA slope - 1N cells', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')
    gss[1].axhline(0, color='black', linewidth=0.5)
    gss[1].set_ylim(-2,2)
    
    print('truncated spearman, x > 0.7 1/min')
    spear_df = spear_df[spear_df.x>=0.7]
    print(spearmanr(spear_df.x, spear_df.y))

ess_rna_df = rna_data[rna_data.gene_ID.isin(gerdes_essential)]
non_rna_df = rna_data[~rna_data.gene_ID.isin(gerdes_essential)]

print(ess_rna_df.shape[0])
print(non_rna_df.shape[0])
ess_kde = sp.stats.gaussian_kde(ess_rna_df.RNA_slope, bw_method='scott')
non_ess_kde = sp.stats.gaussian_kde(non_rna_df.RNA_slope, bw_method='scott')
eval_points = np.arange(-3.5, 3.51, 0.01)
plt.title('Gerdes et al. 2003', fontweight='bold', fontsize=14)
plt.plot(eval_points, ess_kde.pdf(eval_points), color='red', label='Essential')
plt.plot(eval_points, -non_ess_kde.pdf(eval_points), color='gray', label='Non-essential')
plt.axhline(0, linewidth=0.5, color='black')
plt.axvline(0, linewidth=0.5, color='black')
plt.plot([np.quantile(ess_rna_df.RNA_slope, 0.25), np.quantile(ess_rna_df.RNA_slope, 0.25)], [0,0.6], color='red')
plt.plot([np.quantile(ess_rna_df.RNA_slope, 0.75), np.quantile(ess_rna_df.RNA_slope, 0.75)], [0,0.6], color='red')
plt.plot([np.quantile(non_rna_df.RNA_slope, 0.25), np.quantile(non_rna_df.RNA_slope, 0.25)], [-0.4, 0], color='gray')
plt.plot([np.quantile(non_rna_df.RNA_slope, 0.75), np.quantile(non_rna_df.RNA_slope, 0.75)], [-0.4, 0], color='gray')
plt.xlim(-3.5, 3.5)
plt.legend()
plt.xlabel('RNA slope - 1N-rich cells', fontweight='bold', fontsize=14)
plt.ylabel('Probability density - 1N-rich cells', fontweight='bold', fontsize=14)
plt.show()

esential_group  = goodall_essential

non_log_deg= np.log10(non_deg_df.rna_degradation.astype(float)).to_list()                           
print(len(ess_log_deg), len(non_log_deg))

non_ess_kde = sp.stats.gaussian_kde(non_log_deg, bw_method='scott')

plt.plot(eval_points, -non_ess_kde.pdf(eval_points), color='gray', label='Non-essential')
